---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config';
---

<Base title="About">
  <section class="about wrap wrap--narrow">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Why a 21-year-old is covering the wealth transfer</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Over the next two decades, roughly $84 trillion will move from one
        generation to the next — the largest transfer of wealth in history.
        Almost everyone writing about it is on the sending side: advisors,
        estate attorneys, executives. I'm on the receiving side, and I'm
        training to manage it.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm {SITE.author}, a finance and financial planning student at Virginia
        Tech, currently working in wealth management. I've prepared tax returns
        for high-net-worth families, worked with executive equity compensation
        and pension plans at a $4B RIA, and I'm building a career in private
        wealth. Every Sunday, I write about what happened in markets and what
        it means for the generation about to inherit them — for the advisors
        trying to understand their clients' kids, and for my peers trying to
        understand what's coming to them.
      </p>
      <p>
        <!-- Add a photo: put a file named "me.jpg" in the /public folder,
             then remove this comment and uncomment the line below. -->
        <!-- <img src="/me.jpg" alt="Portrait of {SITE.author}" width="320" /> -->
      </p>
      {
        SITE.linkedin && (
          <p>
            Say hello on <a href={SITE.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a>.
          </p>
        )
      }
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
